Class TupleInTupleOut

@InputPorts(@InputPortSet) @OutputPorts(@OutputPortSet(cardinality=1,windowPunctuationOutputMode=Preserving)) public abstract class TupleInTupleOut extends AbstractOperator
Abstract pattern class for an operator that receives a tuple and then optionally submits a tuple. This pattern supports a number of input streams and a single output stream. A sub-class provides optional filtering and transformation.
